    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052520/extras/2bd91d78dee1cbea358d0494e935c1d5.poster.avif?t=1723659996\" width=750 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052520/extras/2bd91d78dee1cbea358d0494e935c1d5.webm?t=1723659996\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052520/extras/2bd91d78dee1cbea358d0494e935c1d5.mp4?t=1723659996\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Volleyborne: Unbound Horizons</strong> is a groundbreaking first-person volleyball game that redefines the sports gaming experience. Built for realism and immersion, Volleyborne brings every aspect of real-life volleyball to your screen with unparalleled precision and detail. From powerful spikes to insane digs, anything you can do on the court, you can do in-game.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052520/extras/0ea56884686cb4b3c76400ecb93bf0ad.poster.avif?t=1723659996\" width=750 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052520/extras/0ea56884686cb4b3c76400ecb93bf0ad.webm?t=1723659996\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052520/extras/0ea56884686cb4b3c76400ecb93bf0ad.mp4?t=1723659996\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><i><strong>What makes Volleyborne Different?</strong></i><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Unmatched Realism:</strong> Enjoy a game designed to mirror the physics and dynamics of actual volleyball, ensuring every move feels authentic and responsive.<br></li><li><strong>Skill-Based Gameplay:</strong> Master the art of volleyball with input-driven mechanics that require precise control and strategy. Every action demands your skill and timing, just like in real life.<br></li><li><strong>Fair Competition:</strong> Compete on an even playing field with no pay-to-win elements. Your success depends entirely on your abilities and tactics.<br></li><li><strong>Immersive Experience:</strong> Dive into the most immersive sports gaming experience ever created. Smooth physics and realistic graphics make you feel like you're truly on the court<br></li><li><strong>Intuitive Controls:</strong> Every action that requires your arms and hands is seamlessly integrated with your mouse, putting the power of professional volleyball moves at your fingertips.</li></ul>.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052520/extras/70fc981e8da5f5c696f075a3d973cd99.poster.avif?t=1723659996\" width=480 height=144 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052520/extras/70fc981e8da5f5c696f075a3d973cd99.webm?t=1723659996\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052520/extras/70fc981e8da5f5c696f075a3d973cd99.mp4?t=1723659996\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Join the competition in Volleyborne: Unbound Horizons and prove your skills in the most authentic volleyball game ever made.",
